DataSource.name: Ventas
DataSource.query: SELECT al.id_acc, al.acc, bba.fid_cty_n IS NULL AS _dom, SUM(IF(r.dt BETWEEN $P{tMesIni} AND $P{tFechaFin}, re.credit - re.debit, 0.0)) AS _bal_per, SUM(IF(r.dt < $P{tFechaFin}, re.credit-re.debit, 0.0)) AS _bal_year FROM fin_rec AS r INNER JOIN fin_rec_ety AS re ON r.id_year=re.id_year AND r.id_per=re.id_per AND r.id_bkc=re.id_bkc AND r.id_tp_rec=re.id_tp_rec AND r.id_num=re.id_num INNER JOIN fin_acc AS a ON re.fid_acc=a.id_acc INNER JOIN fin_acc AS al ON LEFT(a.id_acc, 4)=LEFT(al.id_acc, 4) AND al.lev=1 INNER JOIN erp.bpsu_bp AS b ON re.fid_bp_nr=b.id_bp INNER JOIN erp.bpsu_bpb AS bb ON re.fid_bpb_n=bb.id_bpb INNER JOIN erp.bpsu_bpb_add AS bba ON bb.id_bpb=bba.id_bpb AND bba.id_add=1 WHERE NOT r.b_del AND NOT re.b_del AND r.id_year=$P{nAño} AND r.dt <= $P{tFechaFin} AND ((al.fid_tp_acc_r=3 AND al.fid_cl_acc_r=2 AND al.fid_cls_acc_r=1) OR (al.fid_tp_acc_r = 3 AND al.fid_cl_acc_r = 1 AND al.fid_cls_acc_r = 2)) GROUP BY al.id_acc, al.acc, _dom ORDER BY al.id_acc, al.acc, _dom;

DataSource.name: CuentasMayor
DataSource.query: SELECT al.id_acc, al.acc, SUM(IF(r.dt <$P{tMesIni},re.debit-re.credit, 0.0)) AS _open_bal, SUM(IF(r.dt >=$P{tFechaIni},re.debit, 0.0)) AS _debit, SUM(IF(r.dt >=$P{tFechaIni},re.credit, 0.0)) AS _credit, SUM(IF(r.dt >=$P{tMesIni},re.debit-re.credit, 0.0)) AS _bal, SUM(IF(r.dt < $P{tFechaIniYear},re.debit-re.credit, 0.0)) AS _open_bal_acumulado, SUM(IF(r.dt >=$P{tFechaIniYear},re.debit, 0.0)) AS _debit_acumulado, SUM(IF(r.dt >=$P{tFechaIniYear},re.credit, 0.0)) AS _credit_acumulado, SUM(IF(r.dt >=$P{tFechaIniYear},re.debit-re.credit, 0.0)) AS _bal_acumulado FROM fin_rec AS r INNER JOIN fin_rec_ety AS re ON r.id_year=re.id_year AND r.id_per=re.id_per AND r.id_bkc=re.id_bkc AND r.id_tp_rec=re.id_tp_rec AND r.id_num=re.id_num INNER JOIN fin_acc AS a ON re.fid_acc=a.id_acc INNER JOIN fin_acc AS al ON LEFT(a.id_acc, 4)=LEFT(al.id_acc, 4) AND al.lev=1 WHERE NOT r.b_del AND NOT re.b_del AND r.id_year=$P{nAño} AND r.dt <= $P{tFechaFin} GROUP BY al.id_acc, al.acc ORDER BY al.id_acc, al.acc;

DataSource.name: Compras
DataSource.query: SELECT SUM(IF(r.dt BETWEEN $P{tMesIni} AND $P{tFechaFin}, re.credit - re.debit, 0.0)) AS _bal_mes, SUM(IF(r.dt BETWEEN $P{tFechaIniYear} AND $P{tFechaFin}, re.credit - re.debit, 0.0)) AS _bal_acumulado FROM fin_rec AS r INNER JOIN fin_rec_ety AS re ON r.id_year=re.id_year AND r.id_per=re.id_per AND r.id_bkc=re.id_bkc AND r.id_tp_rec=re.id_tp_rec AND r.id_num=re.id_num INNER JOIN fin_acc AS a ON re.fid_acc=a.id_acc INNER JOIN fin_acc AS al ON LEFT(a.id_acc, 4)=LEFT(al.id_acc, 4) WHERE NOT r.b_del AND NOT re.b_del AND r.id_year=$P{nAño} AND r.dt BETWEEN $P{tFechaIniYear} AND $P{tFechaFin} AND ((al.fid_tp_acc_r=3 AND al.fid_cl_acc_r=1 AND al.fid_cls_acc_r=1) OR (al.fid_tp_acc_r=3 AND al.fid_cl_acc_r=2 AND al.fid_cls_acc_r=2)) AND re.fid_acc <> $P{sCuentaTraspasoCompras};

DataSource.name: CentrosCosto
DataSource.query: SELECT a.id_acc, a.acc, cc.id_cc, cc.cc, SUM(re.debit) AS _debit_year, SUM(re.credit) AS _credit_year, SUM(re.debit-re.credit) AS _bal_year, SUM(IF(r.dt < $P{tFechaFin}, re.debit, 0.0)) AS _debit_per, SUM(IF(r.dt BETWEEN $P{tFechaIni} AND $P{tFechaFin}, re.credit, 0.0)) AS _credit_per, SUM(IF(r.dt BETWEEN $P{tMesIni} AND $P{tFechaFin}, re.debit - re.credit, 0.0)) AS _bal_per FROM fin_rec AS r INNER JOIN fin_rec_ety AS re ON r.id_year=re.id_year AND r.id_per=re.id_per AND r.id_bkc=re.id_bkc AND r.id_tp_rec=re.id_tp_rec AND r.id_num=re.id_num INNER JOIN fin_acc AS a ON re.fid_acc=a.id_acc INNER JOIN fin_acc AS al ON LEFT(a.id_acc, 4)=LEFT(al.id_acc, 4) AND al.lev=1 LEFT OUTER JOIN fin_cc AS cc ON re.fid_cc_n=cc.id_cc WHERE NOT r.b_del AND NOT re.b_del AND r.id_year=$P{nAño} AND r.dt <= $P{tFechaFin} AND (al.fid_tp_acc_r = 3 OR (a.id_acc = $P{sParam1} OR a.id_acc = $P{sParam2})) GROUP BY a.id_acc, a.acc, cc.id_cc, cc.cc ORDER BY a.id_acc, a.acc, cc.id_cc, cc.cc;

DataSource.name: CentrosCostoItems
DataSource.query: SELECT a.id_acc, a.acc, cc.id_cc, cc.cc, SUM(IF(r.dt BETWEEN $P{tMesIni} AND $P{tFechaFin}, re.debit - re.credit, 0.0)) AS sum_mes, SUM(IF(r.dt BETWEEN $P{tFechaIniYear} AND $P{tFechaFin}, re.debit - re.credit, 0.0)) AS sum_acumulado FROM fin_rec AS r INNER JOIN fin_rec_ety AS re ON r.id_year = re.id_year AND r.id_per = re.id_per AND r.id_bkc = re.id_bkc AND r.id_tp_rec = re.id_tp_rec AND r.id_num = re.id_num INNER JOIN fin_acc AS a ON re.fid_acc = a.id_acc LEFT OUTER JOIN fin_cc AS cc ON re.fid_cc_n = cc.id_cc LEFT OUTER JOIN erp.itmu_item AS i ON re.fid_item_n = i.id_item WHERE NOT r.b_del AND NOT re.b_del AND r.id_year = $P{nAño} AND r.dt >= $P{nAño} AND r.dt <= $P{tFechaFin} AND a.id_acc = $P{sCuentaGastosProd} AND cc.id_cc < $P{sCentroCostoRefacturacion} AND i.item_key <> $P{sItemTraspasoGastosProd} ORDER BY a.id_acc , a.acc , cc.id_cc , cc.cc;

DataSource.name: CuentasMayorSaldos
DataSource.query: SELECT al.id_acc, al.acc, al.fid_tp_acc_r, al.fid_cl_acc_r, al.fid_cls_acc_r, SUM(re.debit-re.credit) as sum FROM fin_rec AS r INNER JOIN fin_rec_ety AS re ON r.id_year=re.id_year AND r.id_per=re.id_per AND r.id_bkc=re.id_bkc AND r.id_tp_rec=re.id_tp_rec AND r.id_num=re.id_num INNER JOIN fin_acc AS a ON re.fid_acc=a.id_acc INNER JOIN fin_acc AS al ON LEFT(a.id_acc, 4)=LEFT(al.id_acc, 4) AND al.lev=1 WHERE NOT r.b_del AND NOT re.b_del AND r.id_year=$P{nAño} AND r.dt <= $P{tFechaFin} AND al.fid_tp_acc_r=2 GROUP BY al.id_acc, al.acc, al.fid_tp_acc_r, al.fid_cl_acc_r, al.fid_cls_acc_r ORDER BY al.id_acc, al.acc, al.fid_tp_acc_r, al.fid_cl_acc_r, al.fid_cls_acc_r;

DataSource.name: CuentasNivel2
DataSource.query: SELECT a.id_acc, a.acc, cc.id_cc, cc.cc, SUM(IF(r.dt BETWEEN $P{tFechaIni} AND $P{tFechaFin}, re.debit - re.credit, 0.0)) AS _bal_per, SUM(re.debit-re.credit) AS _bal_year FROM fin_rec AS r INNER JOIN fin_rec_ety AS re ON r.id_year=re.id_year AND r.id_per=re.id_per AND r.id_bkc=re.id_bkc AND r.id_tp_rec=re.id_tp_rec AND r.id_num=re.id_num INNER JOIN fin_acc AS a ON re.fid_acc=a.id_acc INNER JOIN fin_acc AS al ON LEFT(a.id_acc, 4)=LEFT(al.id_acc, 4) AND al.lev=1 LEFT OUTER JOIN fin_cc AS cc ON re.fid_cc_n=cc.id_cc WHERE NOT r.b_del AND NOT re.b_del AND r.id_year=$P{nAño} AND r.dt <= $P{tFechaFin} AND al.fid_tp_acc_r=2 GROUP BY a.id_acc, a.acc, cc.id_cc, cc.cc ORDER BY a.id_acc, a.acc, cc.id_cc, cc.cc;
